<H2 ALIGN=CENTER><!WA0><IMG SRC="http://www.cs.ucsb.edu/~cs110a/rule18.gif" HEIGHT=30 WIDTH=468><BR>
Foundations of Scientific Computing-CS110A</H2>

<H2 ALIGN=CENTER>Fall 1996<BR>
<!WA1><IMG SRC="http://www.cs.ucsb.edu/~cs110a/rule18.gif" HEIGHT=30 WIDTH=468></H2>

<H3><FONT COLOR="#A0522D">Instructor</FONT>: </H3>

<P><B><I><!WA2><A HREF="http://www.cs.ucsb.edu/~tyang">Tao Yang<BR>
</A></I></B><!WA3><A HREF="http://www.cs.ucsb.edu">Department of Computer Science</A>,
