</A>Office hours: TR 10:50-11:50, or by appointment</P>

<H3><FONT COLOR="#A0522D">Topics</FONT>:</H3>

<UL>
<LI>Error analysis. </LI>

<LI>Solving linear/nonlinear equations. </LI>

<LI>Directed methods and iterative methods.</LI>

<LI>Approximation of functions, interpolation. </LI>

<LI>Numerical differentiation and integration.</LI>

<LI>Finite-difference methods for ODE/PDEs. </LI>

<LI>C/Fortran and MATLAB programming for scientific computing. </LI>
</UL>

<H3><FONT COLOR="#A0522D">Schedule</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">:</FONT></H3>

<UL>
<LI><FONT COLOR="#000000">Lecture: </FONT>TR 9:30-10:45, ENGR 1132</LI>

<LI>Discussion: M 11:00-11:50 PHELP 1408, F 10:00-10:50 PHELP 3519</LI>
</UL>

